<p class="pUA1">You can close a <b>BTM</b> item once 
 you are happy with the response you receive from <b>Mindkey 
 Workflow</b>.</p>

<p class="pUA1"><b>Important</b>:&nbsp; Inbox <b>BTM</b> items have a specific closure <b>SLA</b>.  Workflow will send out a reminder 
to close a BTM halfway through the SLA period. If you haven't closed it, once the period expires, Workflow will 
auto-close it and move to the Closed Items folder.  <b>Inbox Item BTMs</b> will initially have a <b>grey flag</b> in the 
bottom right-hand corner.  This flag will turn <b>red</b> when a reminder is sent.</p>

<p class="pUA1">Follow the procedure below to close an Inbox Item:</p>

