<tr>
<td class=tdUAPoint width=4%>1.</td>
<td class=tdUAPoint width=96%>Ensure that the <strong>Inbox Items</strong> folder is displayed.
</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td class=tdUAPoint>2.</td>
<td class=tdUAPoint>Click the required item to select it.
</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td>&nbsp;</td>
